# Sensor D6T driver configuration
#

config SENSOR_D6T
    tristate "Omron D6T MEMS Thermal Sensor support"
    default n
    depends on I2C
    help
      Say Y here if you want to support the Omron D6T series non-contact
      MEMS thermal sensors. These sensors use I2C to provide thermal
      data (1x1, 1x8, or 4x4 pixels) for human detection or temperature
      measurement.

      To compile this driver as a module, choose M here: the
      module will be called d6t.